tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Genes(
  gene_id INT,
  gene_name VARCHAR(255),
  chromosome VARCHAR(10),
  gene_start INT,
  gene_end INT
);

CREATE TABLE ExpressionLevels (
 expression_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 gene_id INT,
 cell_type_id INT,
 expression_level DECIMAL,
 FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES Genes(gene_id),
 FOREIGN KEY (cell_type_id) REFERENCES CellTypes(cell_type_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AnalysisResults (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    study_id UUID,
    gene_symbol TEXT,
    cell_type TEXT,
    result_value FLOAT
);
